dataset.description: Skilled Nursing Facilities (SNFs) provide Medicare Part A SNF services to beneficiaries and must report data on certain measures of quality to Medicare through the Skilled Nursing Facility Quality Reporting Program (SNF QRP).  This file contains national averages on quality measures implemented under the IMPACT Act.
dataset.title: Skilled Nursing Facility Quality Reporting Program - National Data

theme.title: Skilled nursing facilities and nursing homes
